  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A man was killed with 02 kilos of Kerala ganja",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Special Task Force, a person was arrested in Ranwala area of \u200b\u200bDelgoda who was in possession of Kerala ganja and ice drugs worth more than three lakh rupees.",
        "According to information received by the officers of the Special Task Force Intelligence Division, the suspect has been arrested.",
        "Along with the suspect, 02 kg of Kerala ganja, 150 grams of ice drug and 10 grams of 550 mg of drug were taken into police custody.",
        "The suspect, a 43-year-old resident of Weliveriya, was arrested and handed over to the Meghawatta Police Station for further investigation."
      ],
